*Porodicu* smo proveli u prirodi. (We spent our family in nature.)

U nasoj *porodici* ima dosta dece. (In our family there are many children.)

Volim da posetim *porodicu* u Beogradu. (I like to visit family in Belgrade.)

*Porodica* je jedno od najvaznijih stvari u zivotu. (Family is one of the most important things in life.)

Posle skole, moj brat ide kod *porodice*. (After school, my brother goes to the family.)

*Porodici* su nam pomogli da se snaÄ‘emo u novom gradu. (Our family helped us to settle in the new city.)